text: Laurence Paul Godfrey is an archer from Great Britain. He was born on 9 June 1976. Godfrey competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics, 2008 Summer Olympics, and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Larry GodfreyLaurence GODFREY == References == Category:1976 births Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain Category:Living people
